From: Nicolas Michaut <nicolas@yumilab.com>
Subject: [PATCH] ARM: dts: sun8i-h3: add experimental overclock OPP entries
Date: 2026-04-06

Add higher Operating Performance Points for Allwinner H3 beyond the
default 1296 MHz cap. These entries are experimental and require
adequate cooling (heatsink + active fan) and a PMIC capable of
supplying the required voltages.

New OPP entries:
  - 1368 MHz @ 1.40V  (PLL: 24 * 19 * 3 = 1368)
  - 1488 MHz @ 1.44V  (PLL: 24 * 31 * 2 = 1488)
  - 1512 MHz @ 1.46V  (PLL: 24 * 21 * 3 = 1512)

WARNING: Running H3 above 1296 MHz exceeds Allwinner specifications.
Use at your own risk. Silicon lottery applies.

Signed-off-by: Nicolas Michaut <nicolas@yumilab.com>
---
 arch/arm/boot/dts/allwinner/sun8i-h3.dtsi | 18 ++++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 18 insertions(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/allwinner/sun8i-h3.dtsi b/arch/arm/boot/dts/allwinner/sun8i-h3.dtsi
--- a/arch/arm/boot/dts/allwinner/sun8i-h3.dtsi
+++ b/arch/arm/boot/dts/allwinner/sun8i-h3.dtsi
@@ -1,3 +1,4 @@
+// SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0
 /*
  * Copyright (C) 2015 Jens Kuske <jenskuske@gmail.com>
  *
@@ -110,6 +111,23 @@
 			opp-microvolt = <1340000 1340000 1340000>;
 			clock-latency-ns = <244144>;
 		};
+
+		opp-1368000000 {
+			opp-hz = /bits/ 64 <1368000000>;
+			opp-microvolt = <1400000 1400000 1400000>;
+			clock-latency-ns = <244144>;
+			turbo-mode;
+		};
+
+		opp-1488000000 {
+			opp-hz = /bits/ 64 <1488000000>;
+			opp-microvolt = <1440000 1440000 1440000>;
+			clock-latency-ns = <244144>;
+			turbo-mode;
+		};
+
+		opp-1512000000 {
+			opp-hz = /bits/ 64 <1512000000>;
+			opp-microvolt = <1460000 1460000 1460000>;
+			clock-latency-ns = <244144>;
+			turbo-mode;
+		};
 	};

 	soc {
--
2.43.0
